He was invited by
President Obama.

00:01:21.230 --> 00:01:22.940
Duncan-Andrade has
also been ranked

00:01:22.940 --> 00:01:24.980
as one of the nation's
most influential scholars

00:01:24.980 --> 00:01:26.750
