01:30:10.130 --> 01:30:13.080
And she says, there is, mijo.

01:30:13.080 --> 01:30:15.810
He says, who's
fighting, Abuelita?

01:30:15.810 --> 01:30:17.876
She says, the two wolves.

01:30:17.876 --> 01:30:20.780
He says, well, who are
the two wolves, Abuelita?

01:30:20.780 --> 01:30:27.660
And she says, one wolf is rage,
avarice, greed, selfishness,

01:30:27.660 --> 01:30:29.650
violence.

01:30:29.650 --> 01:30:32.400
He says, who's the
other wolf, Abuelita?

01:30:32.400 --> 01:30:41.400
She says, the other wolf is
garino, familia, love, empathy.

01:30:41.400 --> 01:30:43.942
He says, who wins, Abuelita?

01:30:43.942 --> 01:30:48.140
And she says, the one you feed.

01:30:48.140 --> 01:30:51.750
Those wolves are inside
every child you serve.

01:30:51.750 --> 01:30:54.750
They're inside every
person in this room.

01:30:54.750 --> 01:30:57.860
They're inside every staff
member you work with.

01:30:57.860 --> 01:30:59.836
They're there.

01:30:59.836 --> 01:31:03.570
If we can change the wolves
we're feeding in ourselves,

01:31:03.570 --> 01:31:06.950
we will change the wolves
the young people are feeding.

01:31:06.950 --> 01:31:09.810
And when we do that, we're
on the path of the thing

01:31:09.810 --> 01:31:12.180
